spec_data.Name: nodejs-pkginfo
spec_data.Description:
This Node.js module provides an easy way to expose package.json properties.
By invoking the pkginfo module all of the properties in your package.json
file will be automatically exposed on the callee module (ie, the parent
module of pkginfo).
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 03:48:04 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: An easy way to expose properties on a module from a package.json
